creator.description:
a label service to show off who's your (vtuber) oshi is/are, think of it like discord's "role" but it'll only showed to whoever subscribe to this moderation service
contact the owner @primula.moe or @primula.my.id to participate and/or add your oshi

locales.description: Shizuka Rin (静凛) is a female Japanese Virtual YouTuber and a member of NIJISANJI's first generation of Livers along with Tsukino Mito, Higuchi Kaede, Elu, Yuki Chihiro, Shibuya Hajime, Suzuya Aki, and Moira. Within the first generation, she also forms the unit "JK-gumi" (JK組, high school girl group) with Tsukino Mito and Higuchi Kaede.
locales.name: Shizuka Rin

locales.description: Tsunomaki Watame (角巻わため) is a female Japanese Virtual YouTuber associated with hololive, debuting as part of its fourth generation of VTubers alongside Tokoyami Towa, Kiryu Coco, Amane Kanata and Himemori Luna.
locales.name: Tsunomaki Watame

locales.description: A cosplayer, an artist, and a vtuber.
locales.name: Rikotan

locales.description:
Mint Fantôme (ミント・ファントーム), also known as Maid Mint, is an independent female English/Japanese-speaking, Virtual YouTuber that debuted 24 July 2020. After retiring in April 2021, she made a surprise return in April 2024.

She is a ghost maid with a full-time haunting job, but has a lot of free time to watch anime and buy idol goods.
locales.name: Mint Fantôme

locales.description: Shigure Ui (しぐれうい) is a female Japanese Virtual YouTuber and illustrator. She also did the character designs for the light novel series OsaMake and anime series WIXOSS DIVA(A)LIVE.
locales.name: Shigure Ui
